description: Eggstatic brings you delicious organic breakfast on the go all around Fort Lauderdale! All of these ingredients are organic or part of the non GMO project; no hormones or steroids, and produce and humanely raised meats are sourced from local natural farms. The quality of the food we eat affects our environment too! Happy animals and vegetables=Happy tummies. Join the movement!
name: Eggstatic Organic Eats
